The paper deals with image matting, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also involves machine learning techniques for generating the trimap, which falls under the subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves graphics processing for generating the alpha matte, which falls under the subfield of computer graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
